md:
giải nghĩa từ "books" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.
- Books (noun) - Sách
	+ Meaning: A written or printed work consisting of pages glued or sewn together along one side and bound in covers.
	+ Example: "She has a collection of rare books in her library."
	+ Related words: novel, textbook, dictionary, magazine, journal

- Books (verb) - Đặt chỗ, ghi chép
	+ Meaning: To reserve or arrange for something in advance, especially a place or a seat.
	+ Example: "I booked a table at the restaurant for tonight."
	+ Related words: reserve, arrange, schedule, appointment, ticket

Note: Depending on the context, "books" can have different meanings and uses.
